{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"We are going to talk today about the sequel of \"Inconvenient Truth.\""},{"time":5000,"text":"It's time again to talk about \"Inconvenient Truth,\""},{"time":10000,"text":"a truth that everyone is concerned about,"},{"time":12000,"text":"but nobody is willing to talk about."},{"time":14000,"text":"Somebody has to take the lead, and I decided to do it."},{"time":18000,"text":"If you are scared by global warming,"},{"time":22000,"text":"wait until we learn about local warming."},{"time":25000,"text":"We will talk today about local warming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29000,"text":"Important health message: blogging may be hazardous to your health,"},{"time":33000,"text":"especially if you are a male."},{"time":36000,"text":"This message is given as a public service."},{"time":38000,"text":"Blogging affects your posture. We start with the posture."},{"time":42000,"text":"This is the posture of ladies who are not blogging;"},{"time":46000,"text":"this is the posture of ladies who are blogging."},{"time":49000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":53000,"text":"This is the natural posture of a man sitting,"},{"time":56000,"text":"squatting for ventilation purposes."},{"time":58000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":61000,"text":"And this is the natural posture of a standing man,"},{"time":65000,"text":"and I think this picture inspired Chris to insert me"},{"time":68000,"text":"into the lateral thinking session."},{"time":71000,"text":"This is male blogging posture sitting, and the result is,"},{"time":77000,"text":"\"For greater comfort,"},{"time":78000,"text":"men naturally sit with their legs farther apart than women,"},{"time":81000,"text":"when working on laptop."},{"time":82000,"text":"However, they will adopt a less natural posture"},{"time":86000,"text":"in order to balance it on their laps,"},{"time":88000,"text":"which resulted in a significant rise of body heat"},{"time":90000,"text":"between their thighs.\" This is the issue of local warming."},{"time":94000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":95000,"text":"This is a very serious newspaper; it's Times of England --"},{"time":100000,"text":"very serious. This is a very --"},{"time":103000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":105000,"text":"-- gentlemen and ladies, be serious."},{"time":107000,"text":"This is a very serious research, that you should read the underline."},{"time":111000,"text":"And be careful, your genes are in danger."},{"time":119000,"text":"Will geeks become endangered species?"},{"time":121000,"text":"The fact: population growth in countries with high laptop --"},{"time":126000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":128000,"text":"I need Hans Rosling to give me a graph."},{"time":130000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":132000,"text":"Global warming fun."},{"time":133000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":136000,"text":"But let's keep things in proportion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140000,"text":"How to take care in five easy steps:"},{"time":142000,"text":"first of all, you can use natural ventilation. You can use body breath."},{"time":149000,"text":"You should stay cool with the appropriate clothing."},{"time":152000,"text":"You should care about your posture -- this is not right."},{"time":157000,"text":"Can you extract from Chris another minute and a half for me,"},{"time":160000,"text":"because I have a video I have to show you."},{"time":163000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":165000,"text":"You are great. This is the correct posture."},{"time":169000,"text":"Another benefit of Wi-Fi, we learned yesterday about the benefits of Wi-Fi."},{"time":172000,"text":"Wi-Fi enables you to avoid the processor. And there are some enhanced"},{"time":179000,"text":"protection measures, which I would like to share with you,"},{"time":180000,"text":"and I would like, in a minute, to thank Philips for helping."},{"time":186000,"text":"This is a research which was done in '86, but it's still valid."},{"time":189000,"text":"Scrotal temperature reflects intratesticular temperature"},{"time":193000,"text":"and is lowered by shaving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194000,"text":"By the way, I must admit, my English is not so good,"},{"time":197000,"text":"I didn't know what is scrotal; I understand it's a scrotum."},{"time":201000,"text":"I guess in plural it's scrotal, like medium and media."},{"time":205000,"text":"Digital scrotum, digital media."},{"time":207000,"text":"And only last year I recognized that I'm a proud scrotum owner."},{"time":213000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":216000,"text":"And this research is being precipitated by the U.S. government,"},{"time":220000,"text":"so you can see that your tax man is working for good causes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"Video: Man: The Philips Bodygroom has a sleek,"},{"time":227000,"text":"ergonomic design for a safe and easy way to trim"},{"time":230000,"text":"those scruffy underarm hairs, the untidy curls on and around your"},{"time":236000,"text":"[bleep], as well as the hard to reach locks on the underside of your"},{"time":239000,"text":"[bleep] and [bleep]. Once you use the Bodygroom, the world looks different."},{"time":247000,"text":"And so does your [bleep]. These days, with a hair-free back,"},{"time":250000,"text":"well-groomed shoulders and an extra optical inch on my [bleep],"},{"time":255000,"text":"well, let's just say life has gotten pretty darn cozy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261000,"text":"Yossi Vardi: This is one of the most popular viral advertisement of last year,"},{"time":270000,"text":"known as the optical inch by Philips. Let's applaud Philips --"},{"time":273000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":274000,"text":"-- for this gesture for humanity."},{"time":276000,"text":"And this is how they are promoting the product. This is --"},{"time":280000,"text":"I didn't touch it, this is original."},{"time":282000,"text":"Laptop use to solve overpopulation. And if everything failed,"},{"time":289000,"text":"there are some secondary uses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291000,"text":"And then our next talk, our next TED if you invite me"},{"time":298000,"text":"will be why you should not carry a cell phone in your pocket."},{"time":300000,"text":"And this is what the young generation says."},{"time":305000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":309000,"text":"And I just want to show you that I'm not just preaching,"},{"time":312000,"text":"but I also practice."},{"time":313000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":316000,"text":"4 am in the morning."},{"time":317000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":320000,"text":"You cannot use this picture."},{"time":321000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":326000,"text":"Now, I have some mini TED Prizes, this is the Philips Bodygroom,"},{"time":335000,"text":"one for our leader."},{"time":337000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":340000,"text":"Anybody feels threatened, anybody really need it?"},{"time":342000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":345000,"text":"Any lady, any lady? Thank you very much."},{"time":350000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}